{"tid":437514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國推186呎迷你屋 畀露宿者入住","createTime":"2017-10-16T05:27:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-18T06:56:22.000Z","uid":37554,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"a7d9c06bd2f2350bb9a45bf5a40652ace1ae5003","tid":437514,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T05:27:11.000Z","msg":"為了解決英國的露宿者問題，家居設計師從客機頭等機艙和遊艇船艙取得靈感，設計出一種「麻雀雖小，五臟俱全」的可移動迷你房屋，一位18歲露宿街頭的英國青年，成為入住該間名為「iKozie」迷你屋的首位住客。<br />\n<br />\n該間迷你屋以鋼架作結構，前面牆身以松木作飾面，屋頂由綠色波紋鐵組成。迷你屋面積17.25平方米(186平方呎)，裏面設有睡房、設備齊全的廚房、浴室和甚至有一個消閒區。整間屋的造價是4萬鎊(41.4萬港元)，在工場建造，再可由吊機吊放至合適位置，如有需要，可疊高放置。<br />\n這個創新意念的房屋計劃，由「露宿者基金」(Homeless Foundation)營運，「春天房屋協會」(Spring Housing Association)負責日常管理。住客需繳付租金、水費和自行購買食物，希望他們可學會自力更生。<br />\n<br />\n首間「iKozie」迷你屋坐落伍斯特郡巴伯尼市(Barbourne, Worcester)，首位入住的18歲青年已露宿街頭一年。伍斯特郡正研究建立一個共有25間「iKozie」迷你屋的社區，安置青年專才、工人、學生和無家可歸的人。相信這是全球首個此類房屋計劃。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171015/large/1507998527_a624.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171015%2Flarge%2F1507998527_a624.jpg&h=b0cb6d05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171015/large/1507998533_fd0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171015%2Flarge%2F1507998533_fd0c.jpg&h=08b2774a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171015/large/1507998538_5c2f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171015%2Flarge%2F1507998538_5c2f.jpg&h=8aed4e57&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c2b0b39f28174d9e4f7b1a824889e1992716262f","tid":437514,"uid":37554,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T05:27:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171015/large/1507998543_2e5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171015%2Flarge%2F1507998543_2e5d.jpg&h=0a885444&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171015/large/1507998548_1613.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171015%2Flarge%2F1507998548_1613.jpg&h=248f1b7e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b9570832371f58cc82274cfa522802dc57455b67","tid":437514,"uid":28170,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T05:28:13.000Z","msg":"真係做訓街都好過係香港做人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa731495def5b1c1bd9c195f545e8826d172d80b","tid":437514,"uid":26752,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T05:28:33.000Z","msg":"香港人仲衰過英國訓街個d"},{"pid":"5d7f8c3e164e138443b0ae813362d510f791bdd9","tid":437514,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T05:29:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人仲衰過英國訓街個d</blockquote><br />\n面積比英國上述嘅組合屋，唔到三分之一 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29c4a05e95ae6f7c57a9c9608d6958051a5e2d60","tid":437514,"uid":10692,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T05:30:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3fcedef9e3b0b5a5b8c30284414d13742755013a","tid":437514,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T05:31:18.000Z","msg":"CLS! 英國咁撚靚既？<br />\n<br />\n香港科學園貨櫃租金要成皮野！<br />\n<br />\n大埔有D樓 (非劏房), 有D租金都唔駛一皮"},{"pid":"92d3cf6e9991897e9902d7ede4e4c505a446275f","tid":437514,"uid":130513,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T05:31:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"adea2babd2b8f346101fdbd3b2ee2de82de4d910","tid":437514,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T05:31:33.000Z","msg":"<blockq